            <title>[LU-19167] Implement new fault injection method to corrupt LNET payload</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19167</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement a a new fault injection method which can corrupt the LNET payload, so that we can test data corruption scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a corrupt rule can be added/removed/listed using &quot;lctl net_corrupt_add/del/list&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
